{"questionId":"9d845a11-6019-4b88-9309-26d92ced4f70_18","correctAnswer":"10","section":"Math","steps":[{"title":"Multiply the expressions","content":"Combine like terms: $$5x^4+7x^4-2x^4=(5+7-2)x^4=10x^4.$$"},{"title":"Identify b","content":"Comparing $10x^4=bx^4$ gives $b=10$. The answer is <strong>10</strong>."}]}